Comedian Trevor Noah used his win at the MTV Movie and TV Awards to give a shout out to his mom and Donald Trump. Noah took the Best TV Host accolade at the very first MTV Movie and TV Awards held in Los Angeles on Sunday. A smiling Noah took to the stage to accept his award and dedicated the win to his mother Patricia Nombuyiselo Noah. She is a powerful strong black woman who didn t listen when they told her she couldn t be more he said. He also thanked his team at The Daily Show before turning his attention to US President Donald Trump. Thank you to Donald J Trump for the comedy, Noah said. The J stands for Jesus. A lot of people don t know that. Share on Facebook Share Share on Twitter Tweet Share on Google Plus Share